ValueSet-IMMZD2DTDTPPregnancyStartingWit.narrative: This schema validates IRI-formatted codes for the IMMZD2DTDTPPregnancyStartingWith4Doses ValueSet for Decision Table ValueSet. Each enum value includes the system URI in the format {systemuri}#{code} to match JSON-LD enumeration IRIs. Display values are available at http://smart.who.int/immunizations/ValueSet-IMMZD2DTDTPPregnancyStartingWith4DosesVS.displays.json.
